{"tid":751261,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"睇得出正皮吹奏曾蔭權個post果班都係平時唔關心政治既人","createTime":"2018-07-21T16:53:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-22T05:35:51.000Z","uid":32051,"like":63,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"527a7932951c0bb3df2e3f88ddadd8b844c632db","tid":751261,"uid":32051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T16:53:45.000Z","msg":"曾蔭權做過咁多衰野，罄竹難書，佢無689咁毒，唔等於佢唔係仆街冚家產。<br />\n<br />\n吹奏佢果班人，係咪佢時任果陣仲讀緊幼稚園或未出世？<br />\n做緊財爺所謂抗金融風暴更加係笑話<br />\n用過千億儲備去嚇走人，其實係市民埋單，佢講成自己最大成就。<br />\n而仲有班人真係對佢感恩戴德果下好笑<br />\n<br />\n即係話唔係見佢晚年失節，臨老過唔到世咁款就值得可憐同吹奏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢依家既身家仲係好多人唔能夠企及架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你班唔留意政治既人收起你地多餘既同情心俾身邊有需要既人啦<br />\n<br />\n曾爵士邊洗你地可憐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a348ed127b6f1d46fdf3270a7523c8271bb2c45","tid":751261,"uid":19552,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T18:01:35.000Z","msg":"當年高登對佢咬牙切齒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95b4f3d461a178b1a8edc1a2438ec6948ed84807","tid":751261,"uid":32051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a348ed127b6f1d46fdf3270a7523c8271bb2c45","tid":751261,"uid":19552,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T18:01:35.000Z","msg":"當年高登對佢咬牙切齒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T18:03:11.000Z","msg":"今日過千正皮<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28bed237bbab80f256f66fd878f039b0a2466fc3","tid":751261,"uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"95b4f3d461a178b1a8edc1a2438ec6948ed84807","tid":751261,"uid":32051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a348ed127b6f1d46fdf3270a7523c8271bb2c45","tid":751261,"uid":19552,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T18:01:35.